result.execSummary:
The defendant Brianna D Barber was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Brianna D Barber is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Brianna D Barber was found guilty of Battery, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
